dct_title_s: Automobile road from Long Beach to Santa Ana via Naples and Seal Beach
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; E.J.B.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, clubs, sugar companies.
Indicates distances from Long Beach and Santa Ana.
Numbered 305 in bottom right and 42 in right margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
